Its forward momentum...

300
00:16:07,900 --> 00:16:08,860
I know you're awesome

301
00:16:12,020 --> 00:16:12,700
I'm hungry

302
00:16:14,620 --> 00:16:15,300
Let's go home and eat

303
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:17,340
There's no water and
electricity in the house

304
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:20,420
I'll figure something out

305
00:16:26,220 --> 00:16:26,740
I have money

306
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:29,420
Let's go and have a luxury food

307
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:30,380
-Alright
-Let's go

308
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:47,260
So luxurious

309
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:49,020
We bought the instant noodles in a cup

310
00:16:51,180 --> 00:16:52,500
It's not environmentally friendly

311
00:16:53,420 --> 00:16:54,580
You should think about it

312
00:16:54,660 --> 00:16:56,460
when you don't want to wash the bowl

313
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:03,700
Let's buy a dishwasher

314
00:17:04,140 --> 00:17:05,370
I'll get my scholarship in a few days

315
00:17:05,460 --> 00:17:05,940
No way

316
00:17:06,980 --> 00:17:08,570
Why do you always want to buy robot?

317
00:17:09,140 --> 00:17:09,660
Look

318
00:17:10,370 --> 00:17:11,780
We've all bought so many noodles,

319
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,940
rice and pickled mustard

320
00:17:14,460 --> 00:17:16,300
Even if the end of
the world breaks out,

321
00:17:16,740 --> 00:17:18,300
we still can live half
a month more than others

322
00:17:18,850 --> 00:17:20,500
So I think we're capable

323
00:17:20,610 --> 00:17:22,180
to get a dishwasher now

324
00:17:22,850 --> 00:17:23,460
No way

325
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:29,140
I wanted to study the structure

326
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:30,300
of the dishwasher for a long time

327
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:33,100
Look at the parameter

328
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:35,220
High temperature of 70 degrees

329
00:17:35,700 --> 00:17:37,860
Sterilization rate up to 99.99%

330
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:39,580
We have nothing to lose

331
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:43,060
Pick either Circle or dishwasher

332
00:17:57,740 --> 00:17:58,820
Good boy

333
00:18:28,520 --> 00:18:30,560
There are 15 minutes
left before the test

334
00:18:30,560 --> 00:18:31,480
Take your time

335
00:19:26,600 --> 00:19:28,240
Are you ready to move?

336
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:31,760
I'm just free at the end of the project

337
00:19:32,080 --> 00:19:32,600
You?

338
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:34,920
I applied for a delay
in leaving campus

339
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,680
I'll stay in the postgraduate
dorm for temporary

340
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,960
Then I'll send the luggage
directly to the University of North

341
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:40,560
You're not going home, huh?

342
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,040
Fu Pei doesn't allow it

343
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,640
So you listen to him, huh?

344
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:46,600
What if you go to the university later?
Will he cry every day?

345
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:49,120
He wanted to go with me,
but I stopped him

346
00:19:49,280 --> 00:19:49,960
Why?

347
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:53,600
There are preferential policies
under local graduate entrepreneurs

348
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:56,400
If he wants to start a company,
it's better for him to stay here

349
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:59,080
He wanted to start a company, huh?

350
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:03,000
-He has a entrepreneurial mind
-You've been blinded by love

351
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:07,880
So you'll be in a long-distance love

352
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:09,880
Yeah

353
00:20:11,080 --> 00:20:12,320
It's terrible

354
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:13,760
It seems like falling
into the air every day

355
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,000
I'm sure I can't stand it

356
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:18,520
Gu Wei Yi and you
see each other every day

357
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,400
You don't have to worry about that

358
00:20:24,360 --> 00:20:25,280
Shan Shan, look at this

359
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:27,800
When I first got this,
I couldn't fall asleep all night

360
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,600
Now we suddenly graduated.

361
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:33,360
Yeah

362
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:38,240
When Lulu first arrived, she
couldn't even hang a mosquito net

363
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:41,600
She even washed the apple with
laundry liquid and you ate the apple

364
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:42,600
Shan Shan

365
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:46,040
I know we can't be too
sensational at this moment

366
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:48,040
Or we're going to cry

367
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,040
No

368
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:52,120
Look! I made the money when
I worked as a tutor for the first time

369
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:53,760
I hid it to avoid spending

370
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,040
until I forgot it

371
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,720
I'm rich

372
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,480
RMB 800!

373
00:20:58,520 --> 00:20:59,320
So silly!

374
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:00,520
Oh, my God!

375
00:21:05,560 --> 00:21:06,160
Hello

376
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:08,720
I'm done with the test and packing

377
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:12,200
I'm not done yet,
Lu Lu and Niu Niu are not here

378
00:21:12,360 --> 00:21:13,880
I want to have a meal with them first

379
00:21:14,320 --> 00:21:15,120
Take your time then

380
00:21:15,520 --> 00:21:16,720
I'll go to the lab first

381
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,560
Call me when you're okay,
I'll pick you up

382
00:21:20,520 --> 00:21:21,080
Okay

383
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:23,760
Shan Shan

384
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:25,800
When will Lu Lu and Niu Niu come back?

385
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:28,680
Lu Lu went for a movie with Ke

386
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:30,440
Hu Niu went out for
the personnel files

387
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:33,600
It's so hard for me to
have a meal at the canteen

388
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:36,720
I have something to do later,
I can't go with you

389
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:42,080
Make sure you send
the old books to the warden

390
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:43,200
Okay

391
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:51,640
Gu Wei Yi

392
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:53,800
Let's check the answer in the lab

393
00:21:54,520 --> 00:21:56,080
I'll not stay in the lab after this

394
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,480
Are you staying in the lab?

395
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:02,160
Yeah, it's easier for my revision here

396
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:03,640
Prof. Jiang knew about it?

397
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:05,360
He'll surely stop me if he knows it

398
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:08,560
I used to bring the cat to the lab
and he complained a lot

399
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:09,920
You even brought a cat to the lab?

400
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:12,240
Do you know how expensive
the lab instruments are?

401
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:14,000
Can you afford to pay
if anything happens?

402
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:17,840
The lab has its rules, I have to
report this to the university

403
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:19,960
Gu Wei Yi

404
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:25,480
She's going to report to the university
that I was staying in the lab

405
00:22:25,920 --> 00:22:26,760
And you even raise a cat

406
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,760
You'd better be prepared with a review

407
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:31,080
I used to take care of the cat too

408
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:32,960
Gu Wei Yi, don't protect him

409
00:22:33,120 --> 00:22:34,400
I know you were forced by him

410
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:35,200
No

411
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:36,600
You're biased against me

412
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:38,040
Why do you always target me?

413
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:40,720
Why should I? I just
judge the matter as it stands

414
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:43,040
You're biased against me

415
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:45,000
It's not that serious

416
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,200
What?

417
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:49,240
If that's serious, it may affect
your eligibility to go abroad

418
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:50,160
Senior

419
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:52,880
Let's leave it to Prof. Jiang

420
00:22:56,600 --> 00:22:57,440
What happened?

421
00:22:57,880 --> 00:22:59,360
What's going on?

422
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:01,040
Zhou Lei stays in the lab

423
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,720
and even keeps a cat here

424
00:23:05,040 --> 00:23:07,680
Zhou Lei, why are you
messing in the lab again?

425
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:08,800
Prof. Jiang

426
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:11,040
I just did my revision in the lab

427
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:13,920
The lab has its rules and
there are many instruments here

428
00:23:14,040 --> 00:23:14,760
It's okay

429
00:23:15,400 --> 00:23:16,000
I know about it

430
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,000
Leave it to me

431
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:19,560
So what are you going to do with it?

432
00:23:20,600 --> 00:23:22,280
Don't you have to report
it to the university?

433
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:24,440
Senior

434
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:26,760
I have a problem in my experiment

435
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:28,320
-Let's check it out
-What about this...

436
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:29,640
Help me

437
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:31,200
Help her to check it out

438
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:35,520
Zhou Lei

439
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:36,680
Come with me

440
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:45,760
You're right

441
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:47,400
I've been emotional lately

442
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:49,640
I went on a blind date that day

443
00:23:50,040 --> 00:23:51,600
I ran into a parvenu family

444
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:52,920
They're so cocky

445
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:54,840
When we're eating,

446
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:56,400
his girlfriend suddenly came in

447
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,680
and smashed thing

448
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,280
It's really wicked

449
00:23:59,520 --> 00:24:00,160
Really?

450
00:24:00,320 --> 00:24:00,960
Yeah

451
00:24:01,360 --> 00:24:05,000
The cocky man said his son
is the hottest man in our campus

452
00:24:05,360 --> 00:24:06,480
I don't know if you know him

453
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:08,360
Fu Pei from Management school

454
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:09,440
I don't know him

455
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:10,520
Yeah

456
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:12,520
You shouldn't know that kind of guy

457
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,800
He's rude and cocky

458
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,840
We're not on the same level

459
00:24:20,280 --> 00:24:20,800
Excuse me

460
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:34,320
I'm already downstairs

461
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:36,200
I'm right at the school gate

462
00:24:36,440 --> 00:24:36,920
Just a minute

463
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:37,520
Okay

464
00:24:45,080 --> 00:24:45,840
Uncle Fu

465
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:49,880
It's you

466
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:51,880
Why are you here?

467
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:54,480
I'm not here to see you anyway

468
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:57,280
Uncle, you don't even know me

469
00:24:57,480 --> 00:24:58,960
Why do you hate me so much?

470
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,520
I don't even need to know you

471
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:04,920
Fu Pei always finds a flirt
to be his girlfriend

472
00:25:05,760 --> 00:25:07,200
They all like him
all because of my money

473
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:10,640
If you're going to be with him again,

474
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,120
I'm not giving him any money

475
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:13,760
You can't get anything from him

476
00:25:14,360 --> 00:25:14,880
Uncle

477
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:16,120
Are you saying this

478
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:17,640
to insult me

479
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:19,000
or your son?

480
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:21,160
I have no time for you

481
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:23,040
I'm here to see Jian Shi

482
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:27,240
The rascal brought disgrace
on me in the last dinner

483
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:28,920
Uncle

484
00:25:29,520 --> 00:25:31,480
I knew you stopped
me to be with Fu Pei

485
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:33,040
because you don't know me yet

486
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,560
But why don't you

487
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:35,760
even understand Fu Pei?

488
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:38,760
I don't understand him, huh?

489
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:40,520
Who knows him then?

490
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:41,880
You?

491
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:44,960
Do you know he is going
to start his own company?

492
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:46,920
What?

493
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:50,400
It will take less than
one month to close

494
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:55,000
He used the money which he saved
from the winning basketball games

495
00:25:55,520 --> 00:25:56,320
Everyone thought

496
00:25:56,320 --> 00:25:57,760
he's playing with his dad's money

497
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,360
But he didn't ask you

498
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:00,800
for money for so long, did he?

499
00:26:02,120 --> 00:26:03,560
Even if he did, I won't
give him any single cent

500
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:06,240
He used to do every thing quietly

501
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:09,280
But I know he still wishes
for your recognition

502
00:26:10,840 --> 00:26:13,240
Should I recognize him
because he runs a company?

503
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,080
I just want to say that

504
00:26:15,360 --> 00:26:17,440
Fu Pei is much more mature
than what you think

505
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,560
I hope two of you sit down

506
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:21,120
and chat with an open-heart

507
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:23,840
And not solving the problem
by smashing things like that day

508
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:26,440
Shan Shan

509
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:31,640
What are you doing here?

510
00:26:32,120 --> 00:26:33,240
Is this your territory?

511
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:34,840
No

512
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:36,240
Help yourself then

513
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:37,320
Wait a minute

514
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:43,200
I heard you're going to run a company

515
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,600
Why? Are you afraid to compete with me?

516
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:48,280
Get your business license first

517
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:51,360
I did it

518
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:52,400
Sorry

519
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:54,000
Let's go

520
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:59,640
-Did he give you a hard time?
-No

521
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:01,520
He's quite easy going

522
00:27:01,840 --> 00:27:03,120
He's not as scary as you think

523
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:04,200
Easy going?

524
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:06,760
Did he give you money
to get you out of me?

525
00:27:07,520 --> 00:27:08,120
1 million?

526
00:27:08,520 --> 00:27:09,600
No

527
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:12,200
What? Doesn't he have 1 million?

528
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:13,920
He made parvenu in disgrace

529
00:27:18,280 --> 00:27:19,600
Please help me promote it

530
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:21,480
You won't use the books anymore

531
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,160
Right?

532
00:27:22,360 --> 00:27:22,920
Okay

533
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:24,040
Thank you, see you

534
00:27:24,080 --> 00:27:24,560
Okay, bye

535
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:26,040
Can I put the books here?

536
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:28,000
-Put it here and weigh it yourself
-Alright

537
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:29,360
RMB1 per kg

538
00:27:29,560 --> 00:27:30,840
Count yourself

539
00:27:31,280 --> 00:27:32,520
You're learning accounting right?

540
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:35,320
The total is 11.5kg

541
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,320
11.5kg

542
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:43,240
I don't have small change

543
00:27:43,840 --> 00:27:44,480
Keep the change

544
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:46,240
Help me sort it out

545
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:49,600
Please pick out
non textbook for donation

546
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:50,520
Okay

547
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,800
11.5kg

548
00:27:55,320 --> 00:27:55,880
Girl

549
00:27:56,360 --> 00:27:58,800
You didn't back to the dorm
for a long time, right?

550
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:00,280
You found a house outside?

551
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:01,640
You still remember me, huh?

552
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:03,240
Of course

553
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:08,200
You always came back late and
looked unhappy when I scolded you

554
00:28:09,080 --> 00:28:11,000
I was busy with internship back then

555
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:13,360
I knew, people who came back late

556
00:28:13,520 --> 00:28:14,960
were all sent back by a boy

557
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,400
Only you came back on your own

558
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:19,160
Apparently, you're a single
who worked overtime

559
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:21,320
Do you have a boyfriend now?

560
00:28:21,760 --> 00:28:23,640
-What kind of man do you like?
-A scientist

561
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:25,600
You got the right person

562
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:29,360
My husband is doing
scientific researches

563
00:28:29,560 --> 00:28:30,800
He has 2 students

564
00:28:31,120 --> 00:28:32,120
They're quite nice

565
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:34,440
One of them is handsome,

566
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:36,800
but a little silly

567
00:28:36,960 --> 00:28:38,320
But, at your age...

568
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:39,760
I have a boyfriend

569
00:28:42,320 --> 00:28:42,960
That's good

570
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:44,720
I just merely mention it

571
00:28:45,200 --> 00:28:46,440
Actually, you shouldn't

572
00:28:46,840 --> 00:28:48,360
get a scientist as your boyfriend

573
00:28:49,280 --> 00:28:50,920
They always read for a whole day

574
00:28:51,800 --> 00:28:53,440
You can't understand
what he's talking about

575
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:56,800
And they always do weird things

576
00:28:57,560 --> 00:29:00,040
Always suddenly get up from sleeping

577
00:29:00,280 --> 00:29:01,640
to do the calculation

578
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:05,200
And always bring machines home

579
00:29:10,280 --> 00:29:11,280
Are you feeling better?

580
00:29:11,800 --> 00:29:12,800
